{"tid":752133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆&老母嘅習慣有時都好撚煩～","createTime":"2018-07-22T14:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T08:16:43.000Z","uid":176960,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"154ac73f25dcae6c4b00083eee69a0522fa036c1","tid":752133,"uid":176960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T14:11:30.000Z","msg":"1.人地唔沖涼，佢唔去廁所（沖涼最耐都係十分鐘）<br />\n2.whats app voice message完人地又要聽番自己錄音，仲要較到大大聲（唔係撞聾）<br />\n3.開完部電視又唔係睇都算，仲要睇TVB,跟手轉去Viutv 過一陣又話我好轉佢個台<br />\n4.十二點就叫我唔好咁嘈，驚嘈到其他人,純粹正常聲線傾計，況且間屋仲邊有人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW見到佢地仲健健康康都安心，希望佢地之後都係可以開開心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:孝順撚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/221108_63f98d721ac4afb226aaa34e0bd2d3d2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F221108_63f98d721ac4afb226aaa34e0bd2d3d2.png&h=06ff9271&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f57a3fdf9c6ff0181351b8445998fd90d8da848","tid":752133,"uid":191405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:19:59.000Z","msg":"講電話一定要嗌住講<br />\n話因為開心控制唔到<br />\n但真係好撚大聲 成層都知我瀨尿啦屌"},{"pid":"98c9416c08e43e9364816c082e31d162baa09fdd","tid":752133,"uid":175032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:10:20.000Z","msg":"細個一齊住唔多覺<br />\n大個係外國生活左幾年<br />\n返到黎層樓未裝好修痴住佢地住左幾個月<br />\n頂唔順老母煮飯好浪費永遠煮多好多食唔哂又唔肯留返係雪櫃<br />\n老豆退左休開始有啲嗜好買埋一大堆沙煲爛餐返黎擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"